UIDescription.NativeString: Prove your skill in this competitive mode! As you gain points, you'll compete against tougher opponents with similar scores.

Find and restore vehicles abandoned throughout the map to explore the expansive open world and discover new regions.
Battle fierce creatures & hostile players to collect rare items and experience the challenging end-game content such as raids & other exciting world events.

It's a 8v8 Team Deathmatch. Play as either Team Green or Team Purple as you fight for the win!

Choose your loadout, then battle it out to be the first team to reach 25 eliminations.

Presented by TIME, explore D.C. 63, a reimagined Washington, DC where Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. gave his iconic “I Have a Dream” speech. Alongside Fortnite players from all over the world -- listen to this defining civil rights’ moment. 

Tags: adventure, artistic

 Original Map Name: The March Through Time

Attack and Defend strategic points that offer a chance for victory! If not, then next Phase you'll get your chance.
-
Choose between 9 unique Loadouts that have their own unique special abilities and battle it out in a Futuristic Spaceship.

It’s Team Chicken vs Team Lizard in this epic battle between two giant volcanoes!

Earn gold by eliminating other players. Visit the Witch Doctor and the Warrior to purchase powerful items and use your gold to upgrade your weapons.

Find all the torches around the map to unleash the power of your team's Volcano God! 

First team to 10000 points wins!

Tags: 8v8, difficulty: easy, just for fun, team deathmatch

Original Map Name: VOLCANO WARS

Discover attractions and minigames around the map and have some fun in this summer theme park.

Tags: open world, role playing, simulator, teams

Original Map Name: THEME PARK

Battle for gold and climb the leaderboards in this PVP centered Open World LTM by Atlas Creative.
Featuring 1v1s, Boxfighting, FFA, Racing, Fishing and More!

Immerse yourself into the world of Living Room PVP and fight beyond your imagination.
Run around with your friends or solo up and get ready to purchase your next mystery weapon box to show your strength!
